sec.p:
Lines were genotyped for 3,548 SNPs using an insertion site-based polymorphism technique (Paux et al. 2010). After removing SNPs with minor allele frequency smaller than 3 % and SNPs with more than 10 % of missing values, a total of 2,395 SNPs were still available for analysis. The remaining missing genotypes were imputed using \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
